question: retrieve the details of the user whose user name is BHD-186
sql:
SELECT
    user_id,
    user_name,
    user_type,
    first_name,
    last_name,
    birth_date,
    gender,
    is_active,
    login_failures_count,
    enrollment_date,
    is_account_locked,
    roster_user_id,
    created_by,
    date_created
FROM
    application_user
WHERE
    user_name = 'BHD-186'
FETCH FIRST 25 ROWS ONLY

question: show the top 5 recently received recognitions by user whose user name is BHD-191
sql:
SELECT
    c.submission_date,
    rc.behavior,
    rc.submitter_comments,
    sub_user.first_name AS submitter_first_name,
    sub_user.last_name AS submitter_last_name
FROM
    application_user rec_user
JOIN
    claim_recipient cr ON rec_user.user_id = cr.participant_id
JOIN
    claim_item ci ON cr.claim_item_id = ci.claim_item_id
JOIN
    claim c ON ci.claim_id = c.claim_id
JOIN
    recognition_claim rc ON c.claim_id = rc.claim_id
JOIN
    application_user sub_user ON c.submitter_id = sub_user.user_id
WHERE
    rec_user.user_name = 'BHD-191'
order by
    c.submission_date desc
FETCH FIRST 5 ROWS ONLY
